[normal]1.5.2[bold]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]RE-Charge[bold] (2008-2011)[bold]The £2.7m 3 year Council investment programme helped 281 private households 
[normal]across 
[normal]Kirklees, install 296 renewable energy generating technologies. 
[normal] 
