[normal] 95% of survey respondents believed that the world’s climate is ch
[normal]anging
[normal], and 
[normal]74% said that their everyday actions con
[normal]tributed to climate change. 
[normal]86% 
[normal]of respo
[normal]ndents
[normal] also
[normal] 
