[normal], and i)
[normal] 
[normal]s
[normal]aving money,
[normal] ii)
[normal] convenience/services making it easy
[normal],
[normal] and 
[normal]iii) 
[normal]health benefits were 
[normal]the 
[normal]survey respondents' top three motivations to live a greener lifest
[normal]yle
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]2.2
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Utilising these survey results, w
[normal]e are keen to lead the way as a Council by showing our residents that we are investing in measures to tackle climate change but that will also help individ
